      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section id=\"collections\" class=\"rr2-section rr2-collections\"><div class=\"rr2-wrap\"><div class=\"rr2-section-head\"><div class=\"rr2-eyebrow\">Curated collections</div><h2 class=\"rr2-heading\">Packaging families for product stories with a season, a shelf, and a first impression.</h2></div><article class=\"rr2-row\"><div class=\"rr2-media\"><div class=\"rr2-image-placeholder\"><span class=\"rr2-image-mark\">01</span><span>Natural-light food packaging study</span></div></div><div class=\"rr2-copy\"><div class=\"rr2-num\">01</div><div class=\"rr2-label\">Everyday / Food Packaging</div><h3>Food Packaging</h3><p>Rigid cartons, sleeves, and specialty paper structures for products that need to feel considered before they are tasted.</p><a class=\"rr2-link\" href=\"/pages/contact\">Discuss a project</a></div></article><article class=\"rr2-row rr2-row--reverse\"><div class=\"rr2-media\"><div class=\"rr2-image-placeholder\"><span class=\"rr2-image-mark\">02</span><span>Holiday gift-set packaging study</span></div></div><div class=\"rr2-copy\"><div class=\"rr2-num\">02</div><div class=\"rr2-label\">Seasonal / Holiday Gift Sets</div><h3>Holiday Gift Sets</h3><p>Gift-ready packaging systems with tactile papers, foil details, magnetic closure, and a moment of ceremony.</p><a class=\"rr2-link\" href=\"/pages/contact\">Discuss a project</a></div></article><article class=\"rr2-row\"><div class=\"rr2-media\"><div class=\"rr2-image-placeholder\"><span class=\"rr2-image-mark\">03</span><span>Cosmetic advent calendar structure</span></div></div><div class=\"rr2-copy\"><div class=\"rr2-num\">03</div><div class=\"rr2-label\">Countdown / Cosmetic Advent</div><h3>Cosmetic Advent</h3><p>Drawer systems, numbered reveals, and engineered unboxing routes for beauty launches and limited editions.</p><a class=\"rr2-link\" href=\"/pages/contact\">Discuss a project</a></div></article></div></section>",
